Reclusa::

She kept her regal posture. Her hands on her hips, and her head held
up. "Starstorm is it. Well, since you seem to be in need of
information, I shall let you in some knowledge. I have only met him
recently since he was sent to bring me here. Now I have other things
to attend to."
She turned and started down the hall towards the lab.
